LEHIGH VALLEY R. CO. v. UNITED STATES. (Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. May 25, 1911.) No. 286. In Error to the Circuit Court of the United States for -the Western District of New York. Kenefick, Cooke, Mitchell & Bass (James McC. Mitchell, of counsel), for plaintiff in error. John Lord O’Brian, U. S. Atty.

Before LACOMBE, COXE, and WARD, Circuit Judges.'

PER CURIAM.

Judgment affirmed, on the opinion of Judge Holt. 184 Fed. 971.
